OL,3,CHousing Minister lodges plan to
OL,4,Coverhaul Jersey's tenancy laws
OL,6,FJersey's Housing Minister has lodged
OL,7,Fhis plans to dramatically change the
OL,8,Fisland's tenancy laws.
OL,10,FAfter previously revealing some
OL,11,Fdetails, the full amendment to the law
OL,12,Fhas now been announced and Deputy Sam
OL,13,FMezec says it will help "alleviate the
OL,14,Fhousing crises" on the island.
OL,16,FHe adds: "The current law pretty much
OL,17,Fdoesn't have any limits on what
OL,18,Flandlords can do with rent increases.
OL,20,F"The people who should worry are bad
OL,21,Flandlords.
