OL,6,F"I expect they'll be a noisy minority
OL,7,Fwho will be worried about this and
OL,8,Fthey should be because my aim is to
OL,9,Fstop what they are doing."
OL,11,FThe UK's Labour Government has been
OL,12,Fworking on a Renter's Right Bill - the
OL,13,FMinister described his own amendment
OL,14,Fas "Jersey's equivalent".
OL,16,FSome of the main changes include:
