OL,6,FThere are exemptions for rent
OL,7,Fincreases that apply to landlord-
OL,8,Femployers, social housing providers,
OL,9,Frent significantly behind the market
OL,10,Frate, and if the property is improved
OL,11,Fto the tenant's benefit.
OL,13,FDeputy Mezec says his plans would
OL,14,Fprovide "a clearer and fairer
OL,15,Fframework, for both landlords and
OL,16,Ftenants, on how to end a tenancy -
OL,17,Frather than the free for all that we
OL,18,Fcurrently have which can lead to
OL,19,Finjustices".
