OL,4,Coverhaul Jersey's tenancy laws
OL,6,FHe adds: "We don't have a decent
OL,7,Fframework in our tenancy law to
OL,8,Fprotect tenants from extortionate rent
OL,9,Fincreases, from 'revenge evictions'
OL,10,Fand we don't have protections for
OL,11,Ftenants to enjoy a long time in their
OL,12,Fhome without facing uncertainty.
OL,14,F"And probably not a good enough
OL,15,Fframework as well for landlords who
OL,16,Fare doing a decent job and want to
OL,17,Fhave confidence that they can manage
OL,18,Ftheir properties effectively".
