OL,3,CHousing Minister lodges plan to
OL,4,Coverhaul Jersey's tenancy laws
OL,6,FThe draft law will be lodged on
OL,7,FTuesday 25 March and a States' debate
OL,8,Fis planned before the summer break.
OL,10,FIn response, the Jersey Landlords'
OL,11,FAssociation (JLA) says it is
OL,12,F"committed to encouraging landlords to
OL,13,Fbehave responsibly and empowering
OL,14,Ftenants".
OL,16,FIt adds: "The JLA strongly disagrees
OL,17,Fwith the introduction of rent controls
OL,18,Fto Jersey's housing market.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
