OL,3,CHousing Minister lodges plan to
OL,4,Coverhaul Jersey's tenancy laws
OL,6,F"When rent controls are coupled with
OL,7,Fopen-ended tenancies, a landlord may
OL,8,Ffind themselves unable to increase
OL,9,Frent to market value for many years,
OL,10,Fas a tenant may be on a never-ending
OL,11,Flease."
OL,13,FInstead, the Association is calling
OL,14,Ffor government guidance on existing
OL,15,Flegislation before new regulations are
OL,16,Fbrought in, as well as an Approved
OL,17,FCode of Practice setting out what is
OL,18,Fexpected for landlords, tenants and
OL,19,Fagents.
